data.description: Welcome Home! This spacious, well cared for home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and sits on .55 acres. The home features a covered front porch, a rear screened in porch, a fence in yard, and a detached carport. The oversized eat in kitchen has an abundance of cabinetry, ample counter space, and a desk area. Split Bedroom floorplan. The large primary suite has dual closets, and a bathroom with soaking tub. HVAC approx 2 years old. The home has been lovingly cared for throughout the years. MULTIPLE OFFERS - Best & Final offers due 4/21 at 5PM
